history.content:
Based on what has been said about the mathematical maturity necessary for 189, I would highly advise against taking 189 with only 54 under your belt. Ideally, one should have 126 and 127 going into 189, which by association requires having 53, 54, and 70. The lower divs are not enough for 189 alone. Option A looks better. 

----

It's unlikely you would learn much machine learning in 189 without any mathematical maturity, as you'd be spending most of your time just trying to learn the basics of 126/127. Would recommend Option A.
